data.description: Welcome to this charming 2-bed, 1.5-bath Williamstown home with new paint and modern vinyl flooring in select rooms. Move-in ready, well-maintained, and designed for comfort. The updated features, including fresh paint and contemporary finishes, provide a stylish and inviting atmosphere. With two bedrooms and 1.5 baths, and a potential 3rd bedroom on the main floor, this property is both practical and cozy, offering a seamless transition for a comfortable lifestyle. Don't miss the chance to make this your ideal home in the heart of Williamstown.
